data.description: Beautifully renovated 2 Bedroom/2 Full Bathroom, second floor home in a gated community.  Top notch updates include: Fresh custom paint throughout, new kitchen cabinetry, new granite countertops, new luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring, new light Fixtures & new ceiling fans. Mint condition, easy to show & move in ready -- A must see home -- Adjacent to a fenced dog park and public boat ramp. Convenient to Naval Bases, EVMS, ODU and Ghent.
